ref:_00D7091pB._500Q000Bv0oA:ref

Hi Daniel

Issue started around 4 months ago.

We have been working with Dell on the issue but they have not been able to resolve with us.

We tested removing Symantec and EPP on a frequent issue user device, issue stopped.

We then introduced EPP back onto device and the issue started again.

This affects every model we have. Including Dell 7420, 7430, 7440

Thanks
Josh
